Directory service with Microsoft AD.

AWS Directory for Microsoft active directory is powered by an actual Windows server Active directory

There are two types 
standard edition :- upto 5000 users
Entrprise edition :- For large deployments

AD connector
It a proxy service , that provides easy way to connect  applications in cloud to your existing application on-premised AD 
when user logs in to the application, AD connector forwards sign-in requests to your on-premise AD domain controller for authentication


Simple AD
simple AD is a Microsoft Active Directory comptaible directory from AWS direcory service that is powered by Samba4.
simple AD supports basic Active directory features such as user accounts,memberships, joning Linux domains 
Simple AD does not supports trust relationship, DNS dynamic update, schema extentionsm,MFA 
